rows: where $y^{i}=1+\frac{1}{2}\left(x^{i}+1\right)$, and $u\left(x^{i}, a, k, m\right)= \begin{cases}k\left(x^{i}-a\right)^{m} & x^{i}>a \\ 0 & -a \leq x^{i} \leq a \\ k\left(-x^{i}-a\right)^{m} & x^{i}<-a\end{cases}$
